# Ignore everything by default so the public repo only keeps the addon source
# plus the minimal packaging automation files.
*

# Re-include directories so Git can find the explicitly allowed files below.
!*/

# Addon source files.
!*.lua
!*.toc

# Packaging metadata and automation.
!.gitignore
!.pkgmeta
!.github/
!.github/workflows/
!.github/workflows/release.yml
!README.md
!CurseForge/CHANGELOG.md
!CurseForge/DESCRIPTION.md

# Keep local release artifacts out even if created later.
.release/
